<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 10:07:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>没有设备、人员或电力：加沙地带南部的医院因伤病人数过多而不堪重负</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/hospitals-in-southern-gaza-strip-overwhelmed-by-scale-of-wounded-and-ill/0000018c-3e33-d11b-a3bf-febb23d70000</link><description>汗尤尼斯和拉法医院的医生告诉《国土报》，当地情况不断恶化，床位和物资匮乏，并且有可能爆发疾病，导致死亡人数飙升。如果疏散迫在眉睫，医生会问：“我们要去哪里？”我们可以将病人疏散到哪里？</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 09:31:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/hospitals-in-southern-gaza-strip-overwhelmed-by-scale-of-wounded-and-ill/0000018c-3e33-d11b-a3bf-febb23d70000</guid></item><item><title>向汗尤尼斯挺进，以色列军队遭遇加沙战争迄今为止最激烈的战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/sweeping-south-israeli-army-encounters-most-intensive-fighting-of-gaza-war-so-far/0000018c-3bb1-de12-a3af-3bfd0c1e0000</link><description>在加沙地带进行了两个月的战斗后，以色列国防军在汗尤尼斯问题上面临着更加严峻的战斗。 ■ 美国和以色列国防军总参谋部认为，内塔尼亚胡的行动是出于政治动机。知道哈马斯的地下隧道吗？</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 04:00:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/sweeping-south-israeli-army-encounters-most-intensive-fighting-of-gaza-war-so-far/0000018c-3bb1-de12-a3af-3bfd0c1e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙地带南部激战； CNN：美国官员预计战争将持续“数周”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article-live/netanyahu-rules-out-intl-force-in-gaza-cnn-u-s-officials-expect-war-to-last-weeks/0000018c-3d30-d11b-a3bf-ffb996270000</link><description>阿拉伯电视台：以色列军队包围了加沙南部哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔的家 ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告称在约旦河西岸与以色列军队的冲突中受伤 ■ 以色列国防军称周二又有两名士兵被杀 ■ 内塔尼亚胡告诉人质家属“不可能”后，他们感到愤怒立即遣返所有俘虏 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀；加沙仍有超过 138 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙至少有 15,899 人死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 03:45:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-06/ty-article-live/netanyahu-rules-out-intl-force-in-gaza-cnn-u-s-officials-expect-war-to-last-weeks/0000018c-3d30-d11b-a3bf-ffb996270000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-3c6d-d11b-a3bf-feedb31b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 00:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-3c6d-d11b-a3bf-feedb31b0000</guid></item><item><title>共和党议员的反犹太主义模因：国会更关注犹太复国主义而不是美国爱国主义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/gop-lawmakers-antisemitic-meme-congress-more-focused-on-zionism-than-american-patriotism/0000018c-3c36-d5f2-a5cc-7e368fc40000</link><description>众议员托马斯·马西是唯一投票反对谴责美国反犹太主义抬头决议的共和党人</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 23:27:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-06/ty-article/.premium/gop-lawmakers-antisemitic-meme-congress-more-focused-on-zionism-than-american-patriotism/0000018c-3c36-d5f2-a5cc-7e368fc40000</guid></item><item><title>什么时候你才能明白？领导层需要女性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-will-you-understand-women-are-needed-in-leadership/0000018c-3ba1-dc03-a9ec-3ffb112f0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 22:27:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-will-you-understand-women-are-needed-in-leadership/0000018c-3ba1-dc03-a9ec-3ffb112f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对待以色列妇女就像对待孩子一样</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-treats-israeli-women-like-children/0000018c-3ba0-d11b-a3bf-ffa9ff400000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 22:24:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-treats-israeli-women-like-children/0000018c-3ba0-d11b-a3bf-ffa9ff400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府甚至在战前就正在破坏经济</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/this-israeli-government-was-damaging-the-economy-even-before-the-war/0000018c-3ba8-d5f2-a5cc-7fbcf2410000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 22:02:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-12-06/ty-article-opinion/this-israeli-government-was-damaging-the-economy-even-before-the-war/0000018c-3ba8-d5f2-a5cc-7fbcf2410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对红十字会的愤怒反映了本尼·甘茨的政治问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israeli-anger-at-the-red-cross-reflects-benny-gantzs-political-problems/0000018c-3ba1-de12-a3af-3bed376c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 21:50:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israeli-anger-at-the-red-cross-reflects-benny-gantzs-political-problems/0000018c-3ba1-de12-a3af-3bed376c0000</guid></item><item><title>自10月7日哈马斯-以色列战争爆发以来，超过100万美国人参加了抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/more-than-1-million-americans-participated-in-protests-since-oct-7/0000018c-3bda-d11b-a3bf-fffbed7b0000</link><description>根据最近的一项研究，大多数声援以色列的集会都集中在 10 月 7 日哈马斯恐怖袭击后的第一周，而声援加沙的行动吸引了更多的人群，并继续在全国范围内蔓延。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 21:44:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/more-than-1-million-americans-participated-in-protests-since-oct-7/0000018c-3bda-d11b-a3bf-fffbed7b0000</guid></item><item><title>对于某些人来说，他还不够犹太人。本周他为以色列而死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/for-some-he-wasnt-jewish-enough-this-week-he-died-for-israel/0000018c-3ba0-d11b-a3bf-ffa9dff00000</link><description>州立宗教学校系统官员对一名来自埃塞俄比亚的六岁移民的犹太身份表示怀疑。十四年后，那个因为族裔而被迫等待学校录取的男孩，成为了一名勇敢的战士</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 21:24:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/for-some-he-wasnt-jewish-enough-this-week-he-died-for-israel/0000018c-3ba0-d11b-a3bf-ffa9dff00000</guid></item><item><title>大学校长因哈马斯-以色列战争引发的校园反犹太主义而受到美国立法者的严厉谴责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/college-presidents-excoriated-by-u-s-lawmakers-over-campus-antisemitism/0000018c-3b44-de12-a3af-3bcd7add0000</link><description>所有三所大学校长都坚决谴责反犹太主义，并采取了详细的措施来打击反犹太主义，但立法者利用听证会谴责他们的努力，一名共和党成员质疑大学多元化举措是否与“马克思主义、BLM、Antifa 仇恨团体”挂钩</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 20:31:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/college-presidents-excoriated-by-u-s-lawmakers-over-campus-antisemitism/0000018c-3b44-de12-a3af-3bcd7add0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙地带南部哈马斯枢纽汗尤尼斯市发起地面行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-initiates-ground-operation-in-khan-yunis-hamas-hub-in-southern-gaza-strip/0000018c-3ae3-d11b-a3bf-feeb33320000</link><description>哈马斯高级人物和许多总部都位于汗尤尼斯，据估计，这里是该组织在加沙地带的部队指挥地。以色列国防军一名高级指挥官表示，过去24小时的战斗是“战争开始以来最激烈的”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 19:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-initiates-ground-operation-in-khan-yunis-hamas-hub-in-southern-gaza-strip/0000018c-3ae3-d11b-a3bf-feeb33320000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质告诉内塔尼亚胡的战时内阁，哈马斯扣押的俘虏遭受饥饿和性侵犯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-tell-war-cabinet-that-hamas-held-captives-suffered-hunger-sexual-assault/0000018c-3abd-dc03-a9ec-3efff69c0000</link><description>作为以色列与哈马斯协议的一部分而被释放的人质分享了有关其对待俘虏的严厉证词。然而，他们的主要批评是针对政府的：“感觉好像你根本不知道那里发生了什么。”你声称有情报，但事实是我们被轰炸了”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 19:33:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-tell-war-cabinet-that-hamas-held-captives-suffered-hunger-sexual-assault/0000018c-3abd-dc03-a9ec-3efff69c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军法院因未对被枪杀的以色列平民进行尸检而怀疑士兵的定罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/court-doubts-soldiers-conviction-due-to-missing-autopsy-of-fatally-shot-israeli-civilian/0000018c-3a80-dc03-a9ec-3efb65860000</link><description>一名以色列陆军法官延长了对阿维亚德·弗里贾的拘留期限，他被指控犯有鲁莽杀人罪，预计将被释放并软禁。法官表示，他认为嫌疑人的行为是非法的，但这样做是由于“无心之失”，他认为以色列受害者是恐怖分子</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 18:40:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/court-doubts-soldiers-conviction-due-to-missing-autopsy-of-fatally-shot-israeli-civilian/0000018c-3a80-dc03-a9ec-3efb65860000</guid></item><item><title>美国对在西岸针对巴勒斯坦平民实施暴力的以色列定居者实施签证禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/u-s-imposes-visa-ban-on-israeli-settlers-engaged-in-violence-against-w-bank-palestinians/0000018c-3b10-d5f2-a5cc-7f14eb790000</link><description>预计相关定居者的名字不会被公开，这表明美国官员希望利用此举的私人性质——这是美国数十年来对以色列采取的最严厉的惩罚措施——作为未来制裁的威慑和威胁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 18:08:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/u-s-imposes-visa-ban-on-israeli-settlers-engaged-in-violence-against-w-bank-palestinians/0000018c-3b10-d5f2-a5cc-7f14eb790000</guid></item><item><title>“我们不能强行进入”：红十字会直面以色列人质事件的愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-12-05/ty-article-podcast/we-cant-force-our-way-in-the-red-cross-confronts-israeli-anger-over-hostages/0000018c-3a54-d5f2-a5cc-7e54eeb50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 17:19:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-12-05/ty-article-podcast/we-cant-force-our-way-in-the-red-cross-confronts-israeli-anger-over-hostages/0000018c-3a54-d5f2-a5cc-7e54eeb50000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗将美国拖入间接冲突，却没有为此付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/iran-managed-to-draw-the-u-s-into-an-indirect-conflict-without-paying-a-price-for-it/0000018c-3a61-d11b-a3bf-fee9cfad0000</link><description>德黑兰将其军事反应限制在“独立”代理人的战略使其具有否认性，即使没有人相信，也可能成为阻止美国对其发动攻击的因素。矛盾的是，华盛顿很乐意接受这一主张，以避免更广泛的地区战争</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 16:15:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/iran-managed-to-draw-the-u-s-into-an-indirect-conflict-without-paying-a-price-for-it/0000018c-3a61-d11b-a3bf-fee9cfad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方批准极右翼游行集会，要求“犹太人完全控制”圣殿山</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-far-right-plans-to-march-on-temple-mount-demand-end-of-waqf-control-of-compound/0000018c-3a3c-d11b-a3bf-febdfd150000</link><description>这次游行计划在光明节前夕举行，被称为“马卡比游行”，以纪念古代犹太人的叛乱。哈马斯领导人哈尼亚将 10 月 7 日的“阿克萨洪水”袭击与犹太人在圣地的存在联系起来</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 15:26:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-far-right-plans-to-march-on-temple-mount-demand-end-of-waqf-control-of-compound/0000018c-3a3c-d11b-a3bf-febdfd150000</guid></item><item><title>假婴儿，真正的恐怖：加沙战争的 Deepfake 增加了人们对人工智能误导能力的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/deepfakes-from-the-gaza-war-increase-fears-about-ais-power-to-mislead/0000018c-3a07-dc03-a9ec-3e7fadf10000</link><description>社交媒体上的账户正在利用人工智能传播有关以色列-哈马斯战争的错误信息。专家担心这对冲突的未来意味着什么</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 13:43:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/deepfakes-from-the-gaza-war-increase-fears-about-ais-power-to-mislead/0000018c-3a07-dc03-a9ec-3e7fadf10000</guid></item></channel></rss>